    <entry>
      <title>Matlab与CCS的数据“交流”</title>
      <link href="/2023/09/06/MatlabDataInputAndOutput/"/>
      <url>/2023/09/06/MatlabDataInputAndOutput/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>最近因为 dsp 的课设而头痛欲裂，就在刚才我在 AI 的帮助下终于找到了 Matlab 数据导入 CCS 的方法。废话不多说直接上代码</p><hr><h3 id="程序代码"><a href="#程序代码" class="headerlink" title="程序代码"></a>程序代码</h3><h4 id="Matlab-导出-dat-文件格式的数据"><a href="#Matlab-导出-dat-文件格式的数据" class="headerlink" title="Matlab 导出.dat 文件格式的数据"></a>Matlab 导出.dat 文件格式的数据</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Frequency_in = 1000;    %需要引入的干扰正弦波的频率</span><br><span class="line">size_cut = 100000;   %截断到多少点</span><br><span class="line">[data,fs] = audioread</span><br><span class="line">result_Fs = 8000;   %结果的采样率(&#x27;C:\Users\kirit\Documents\MATLAB\CCS_music_filter-main\music.mp3&#x27;);  %改成你自己的路径</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">%注意，如果是两个或者以上声道的音频数据，以下代码只取读进来的第一个声道</span><br><span class="line">temp = data(1:size_cut,1);  %由于DSP处理速度过低，要压缩数据</span><br><span class="line">temp2 = resample(temp,result_Fs,fs); %对原音频的再次采样</span><br><span class="line">[size_data,~] = size(temp2);    %求取音频长度</span><br><span class="line">%给音频人为地添加干扰，干扰的频率由Frequency_in给定</span><br><span class="line">noise = sin(2*pi*Frequency_in*size_data/result_Fs*linspace(0,1,size_data));</span><br><span class="line">temp2 = temp2 + noise&#x27;; %加入噪声</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">temp3 = int32(temp2*10^4);  %把数据处理成整形，方便DSP读入</span><br><span class="line">%以下便是关键部分了</span><br><span class="line">fp1 = fopen(&#x27;_input.dat&#x27;,&#x27;wt&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(fp1,&#x27;1651 1 0 0 0\n&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">for i = 1:size(temp3)</span><br><span class="line">    %一开始用的这个方法，但是十六进制是指数形式</span><br><span class="line">    %fprintf(fp1,&#x27;0x%X\n&#x27;,temp3(i));</span><br><span class="line">    %先转化为十六进制在直接输出字符，这样就不会出现指数形式</span><br><span class="line">    fprintf(fp1, &#x27;0x%s\n&#x27;, lower(dec2hex(temp3(i))));</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br><span class="line">fclose(fp1);</span><br><span class="line">%sound(temp4,result_Fs);     %播放处理结果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Matlab-读取-dat-文件格式的数据"><a href="#Matlab-读取-dat-文件格式的数据" class="headerlink" title="Matlab 读取.dat 文件格式的数据"></a>Matlab 读取.dat 文件格式的数据</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Id = fopen(&#x27;C:\Users\kirit\Documents\MATLAB\CCS_music_filter-main\_output.dat&#x27;,&#x27;r&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">data = fscanf(Id,&#x27;%d&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">data = data/10^4;</span><br><span class="line">sound(data,8000);   %播放时，注意采样率需要与生成时一致</span><br><span class="line">fclose(Id);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="结语"><a href="#结语" class="headerlink" title="结语"></a>结语</h3><p>CCS 滤波器还在解决中，汇编真的好难。。。</p><hr>]]></content>
      
      
